et, which he rolled in for eagle.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the par\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"his second shot\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"four feet\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"eagle\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FULL LEADERBOARD \\\"It felt great.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just to finish off the way I finished after that bad break on 15 just makes dinner taste so much better,\\\" Kim said.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9635842861487943, \"rank\": 0.02054158102621849, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"that bad break\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously I have made a few mistakes this week but those little things are coming together to back up those mistakes.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few mistakes\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"those little things\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"those mistakes\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would be special (to win in my homeland).\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my homeland\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be more special because I have not played back at home since I got to the PGA Tour, so to be able to have a good round tomorrow and finish it off would be really special.\\\"\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1188,